{
  "id": "adv_bond_rei_01_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "もう、ほんっとにうちのお父さんて\nなんでああも分からず屋なのかしら……あむ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously‚ I wonder why my dad\nis so clueless… yum",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 12.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ひはしぶりに話すのに……あむあむあむ……勉強の\n心配ばっかり。少しぐらい、信頼してくれてもいいのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We finally had a chance to talk… yum yum yum… Just\nworry about my studies. I wish he could trust me‚ a little more",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.5666670482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、このメガトン苺パフェもう一つください！\nあむ……沙季なら分かってくれるわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ could I please have another Megaton Strawberry Parfait?\nYum… you understand me‚ Saki?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 30.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 36.8666670482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、そうですね。確かに、毎回小言を\n言われるのは、気持ちのいいものではありませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ yes. Truely‚ being nagged\nevery time isn't a pleasant experience",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.5000013988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、たぶんお父様としては\nただ怜ちゃんとお話がしたいんだと思いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I think from your father's point of view‚\nhe just wanted to talk you‚ Rei-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5000013988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 54.0000013988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ひさびさに会うし、どう話題を振ったらいいか分からず\nそういう会話になってしまうんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it's been a while‚ he probably doesn't know what to talk about‚\nthe conversation ended up being like that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0000013988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 61.0333347321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "あむ……。そうなのかしら\n沙季のとこはどうなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yum… Is that so\nWhat about your family‚ Saki?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.0333347321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 69.6000013988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "うちの場合は、心配されることは少ないですけど\nなんというか……応援が熱心過ぎて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My father don't worry about me much‚ but\nwhat should I say… he's cheering me on so hard",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6000013988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "スマホには、私のストラップをつけていますし\n机には、千紗のアクリルスタンドを飾っているみたいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He carries my strap‚ around on his smartphone\nand his desk is decorated‚ with an acrylic stand of Chisa",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9000039419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.5333372753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "しかもこの間なんて、握手会の列に並んでいたんです\n様子を見に来た、って言ってましたけど、恥ずかしくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And the other day‚ he was even standing in line for a handshake event\nHe said he came to see how I was doing‚ but I was embarrassed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5333372753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 95.6666680654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "あー……こう言うとあれだけど、子供の発表会とかで\nはしゃいじゃうタイプなのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahー… It's a bit strange to say this‚ but when I was little‚ my dad was\nthe type to get excited at places like recitals…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6666680654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.3666589101
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "私も、もしお父さんが並んでて\n握手しないとってなったら、恥ずかし過ぎるかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If my dad were standing in line\nand had to shake hands‚ I'd be very embarrassed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3666589101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 114.6666620891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "今日は付き合ってくれてありがとね\n沙季って聞き上手だから、ついいろいろ話しちゃうわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for hanging out with me today\nSaki listens well‚ so I ends up talking about a lot of things",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7666492462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 123.0333159129
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ\nこうしておしゃべりするのは、楽しいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's okay\nBecause it's fun to chat‚ like this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0333159129,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10433.350753800014
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ\nえっと……アップルパイが一つと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right\nUmm… one apple pie and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4333164214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 130.6333292643
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.066650772
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "いいわよ、計算しなくて。ほとんど私が食べたものだし\n私が出すわ。だいぶ愚痴っちゃった分、特別にね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay‚ you don't have to pay. I ate almost all of it\nI'll pay. I've been complaining a lot‚ especially",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.066650772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 146.2999841053
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、これはお会計じゃなくて\nカロリーを記録しているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that's not the bill\nI'm just recording the calories",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2999841053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "前までは帰ってから記録していたんですが\n忙しいと忘れてしまうこともあったので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before‚ I used to record them after I got home\nBut I often forgot when I was busy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.3999780018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 157.8333113352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに怜ちゃんは、メガトン苺パフェが\n820kcal。フレンチトーストが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For your reference‚ Rei-chan's Megaton Strawberry Parfait\nis 820kcal. French toast is—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8333113352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 164.0999851226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "や、やめて沙季！　言わないで！\n今日は特別！　特別だからっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Stop‚ Saki! Don't say that!\nToday is special! It's a special day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.0999851226,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}